item.title: Jdk help please
item.dc:creator: @Slivion Slivion
item.description:
@Slivion wrote:

Don’t remove the quotes, they’re needed. I’ve already gone through this with you. Search for a tutorial on setting classpaths. Also download Java Development Kit (JDK) and Java Runtime Environment (JRE). There is no need to bump this thread or make two of the same topics. Be patient until a helpful member of the community responds.
